I steal bases, 
I don't steal wallets.

32
00:03:27,290 --> 00:03:28,560
That's great and all.

33
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:33,000
Hey, Kunimi !

34
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,520
Fune ?

35
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:37,960
Don't you dare give 
up any hits to him !

36
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:40,600
We have to win this game no matter what kind of hand we're dealt !

37
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,430
Got that ?

38
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:45,800
But I can only deal 
with this hand of mine.

39
